# Output directory for the weekly Umbrel-catalog sync — see
# .github/workflows/sync-umbrel-catalog.yml and docs/architecture/
# community-catalog.md. The sync workflow populates `Apps/<id>/` under
# this directory; this .gitkeep file ensures the directory exists in
# the repo before the first sync runs so dev workflows + package-linux.sh
# don't trip on a missing dir.
